"детали при высоком уровне шума."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid "noise"
msgstr "noise"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Snow, hiss, and dropouts.** Controls grain strength, "
