# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:385
msgid ""
"**Subtle “home video”**: ``tracking=0.25``, ``bleed=0.20``, "
"``softness=0.20``, ``noise=0.25``, ``stripe=0.10``, ``static_bands=0.05``."
msgstr ""
"**Незаметное «домашнее видео»**: ``tracking=0.25``, ``bleed=0.20``, "
"``softness=0.20``, ``noise=0.25``, ``stripe=0.10``, ``static_bands=0.05``."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:386
msgid ""
"**Bad tracking / head clog**: ``tracking=0.8–1.0``, ``stripe=0.6–0.9``, "
"``noise=0.6–0.8``, ``static_bands=0.4–0.6``, ``softness<=0.2``, and set "
