"``noise=0.6–0.8``, ``static_bands=0.4–0.6``, ``softness<=0.2``, и установите "
"``bleed`` примерно в 0.3."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:387
msgid ""
"**Color fringing only**: raise ``bleed`` (about 0.5) and keep other controls "
